ealy（左）和 The Japanese House 的 Amber Bain（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The1975-The-Japanese-House-support-act-UK-Still-At-Their-Very-Best-tour.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The1975-The-Japanese-House-support-act-UK-Still-At-Their-Very-Best-tour-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The1975-The-Japanese-House-support-act-UK-Still-At-Their-Very-Best-tour-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The1975-The-Japanese-House-support-act-UK-Still-At-Their-Very-Best-tour-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The1975-The-Japanese-House-support-act-UK-Still-At-Their-Very-Best-tour-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The1975-The-Japanese-House-support-act-UK-Still-At-Their-Very-Best-tour-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-japanese-house">Japanese House</a>已宣布为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a>即将举行的英国头条巡演提供支持。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matty-healy">马蒂·希利</a>等人将于下个月开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-announce-2024-uk-european-still-at-their-very-best-tour-buy-tickets-3491491">他们的“Still…At Their Very Best”巡演</a>。演出包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-add-fourth-show-at-londons-the-o2-to-sell-out-2024-tour-3496122">在伦敦 O2 剧场举行四晚，</a>以及在格拉斯哥、曼彻斯特和伯明翰停留。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/the-1975-cover-interview-2022-being-funny-in-a-foreign-language-3328010"><em>NME</em>大读物 – 1975 年：“我宁愿成为假装的超级恶棍，也不愿成为假装的英雄”</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（1 月 12 日），The Japanese House（又名 Amber Bain）已确定将在音乐会上为乐队开场。该艺术家与 The 1975 的唱片公司 Dirty Hit 签约，并且之前曾与该乐队合作过。</p><p>她 2019 年的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/japanese-house-good-at-falling-review-2455260">《Good At Falling》</a>由乐队鼓手 George Daniel 联合制作，2023 年的后续专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-japanese-house-in-the-end-it-always-does-review-3462887">《In The End It AlwaysDos》</a>也是如此。此外，希利还为后一张专辑中的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-japanese-house-teams-up-with-the-1975s-matty-healy-for-new-single-sunshine-baby-listen-here-3444993">“Sunshine Baby”</a>献声。</p><p>去年夏天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-announce-massive-summer-2023-london-finsbury-park-show-buy-tickets-3397516">The Japanese House 支持 The 1975 在伦敦芬斯伯里公园举行的大型户外演出</a>。丹尼尔在开场时为艺术家打鼓。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> 。 <a href="https://twitter.com/Japanesehouse?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@ Japanesehouse</a>将支持<a href="https://twitter.com/the1975?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@the1975</a>的“仍然……处于最佳状态”2024 年英国巡演<a href="https://t.co/9hGSJh6ogo">pic.twitter.com/9hGSJh6ogo</a></p><p> - 肮脏的打击 (@DirtyHit) <a href="https://twitter.com/DirtyHit/status/1745748776814256269?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 1 月 12 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>去年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-japanese-house-and-matty-healy-cover-shania-twains-it-only-hurts-when-im-breathing-3460007">贝恩与希利合作现场翻唱了仙妮亚·唐恩的歌曲《It Only Hurts When I&#39;m Breathing》</a> 。</p><p>后来，她在希利于 2023 年出现在<em>亚当·弗里德兰秀</em>中后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-japanese-house-wrote-the-1975-matty-healy-a-really-long-message-about-controversial-podcast-appearance-3462560">谈到了围绕这位歌手的争议。</a>贝恩透露，在听到希利的言论后，她给希利发了一条“非常长”的信息，表达了她对他所说的话的“异议”。</p><p> 1975 年的“Still…At Their Very Best”2024 年英国巡演定于 2 月 8 日在格拉斯哥拉开帷幕。您可以在下面查看完整的时间表，并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/the-1975-tickets/artist/1765575?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=zdmQRZTfwxyNUAZWPp1MB0h4UkFyBqTJnTmkXI0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处找到任何剩余的门票</a>。</p><p> <strong>1975 将演奏：<br /></strong></p><p><strong>二月<br />08 – OVO Hydro，格拉斯哥<br />09 – OVO Hydro，格拉斯哥</strong><br /><strong>12 – O2，伦敦</strong><br /><strong>13 – O2，伦敦<br />14 – O2，伦敦<br />17 - 曼彻斯特，AO 竞技场</strong><br /><strong>18 - 曼彻斯特，AO 竞技场<br />20 – O2，伦敦<br />21 - 名胜世界竞技场，伯明翰</strong></p><p>主唱 Healy <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/the-1975-cover-interview-2022-being-funny-in-a-foreign-language-3328010">在接受<em>NME</em> 2022 年封面采访时</a>解释说，“At Their Very Best”巡演名称的灵感来自于他们作为乐队的成长。 <strong style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;"><br /></strong></p><p> “当我做出<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/1975-brief-inquiry-online-relationships-review-2404007">‘简短的询问……’</a>时，我们长大了一些，”他说。 “The 1975 继续成长的想法并不令人恐惧，因为它并不缺乏性感。现在这是我们最性感的事情。这就是为什么这次巡演被称为“最佳状态”。我们的事情已经解决了。”</p><p> Healy 去年 9 月证实， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-matty-healy-announces-indefinite-hiatus-from-shows-after-current-tour-ends-3504878">The 1975 在英国和欧洲结束“Still…At Their Very Best”演出后，将“无限期中断”现场演出</a>。</p><p>去年 11 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-share-at-their-very-best-live-album-and-announce-vinyl-edition-3532915">，The 1975 发行了一张现场专辑，收录了 2022 年在纽约举行的“At Their Very Best”音乐会</a>。</p><p>圣诞节期间， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-matty-healy-teases-potential-album-and-shares-unreleased-demos-3563768">希利在社交媒体上调侃了新的《The 1975》唱片或个人唱片的可能性</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-japanese-house-confirmed-to-support-the-1975-on-2024-uk-tour-3569805">The Japanese House 确认支持 The 1975 on 2024 UK 巡演的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
